snippet.title: Descent 3 Mercenary part 1 (No commentary)
snippet.description:
There has been a bug issue on youtube that some of the videos I post will only play at fps 30 instead 60 fps which I never seen this happen before.

Descent series are a lot better than the new star wars games.
